         <div xml:lang="grc" type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><ab>
    <lb n="1"/>Ὀρσενοῦπις Νείλωι τῶι 

    <lb n="2"/>ἀδελφῶι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 12.13"><supplied reason="lost">οἵ</supplied>ᾳ</lem><rdg resp="BL 1.46"><supplied reason="lost">τῇ</supplied> <expan>α<ex>ὐτῇ</ex></expan></rdg><rdg><gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>α</rdg></app> ἡμέρᾳ, ἐὰν <unclear>κο</unclear>μ<supplied reason="lost">ί</supplied>σῃ τὴν 

    <lb n="4"/><unclear>ἐπ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>στολήν, ὕπαγε ὅπου 

    <lb n="5"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="BL 12.13"><supplied reason="lost">ἐὰν ᾖ</supplied></lem><rdg><supplied reason="lost">ἐστὶ</supplied></rdg></app> Θᾶυς, ἵνα πέμψῃς 

    <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">αὐτὸ</supplied>ν πρὸς ἐμ<unclear>ὲ</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/>θ<gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/><unclear>ν</unclear>ου 

    <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> <choice><reg>ἐπεὶ</reg><orig>ἐπὶ</orig></choice> χρείαν αὐτοῦ ἔχω 

    <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> <app type="editorial"><lem resp="BGU 2 p.356">ὅτε γ<supplied reason="lost">ὰ</supplied><unclear>ρ</unclear> ἦν</lem><rdg>οτε<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><unclear>ρ</unclear>ην</rdg></app> <app type="editorial"><lem resp="PN M. G. Elmaghrabi (from photo)"><del rend="erasure"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/></del><add place="above">ὧ</add>δε</lem><rdg><add place="above">ω</add><del rend="erasure"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="3" unit="character"/></del></rdg></app>

    <lb n="9"/>εμ<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ο<add place="above">ὔ</add>πω εἰς τὸν κ<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>ν 

    <lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/><unclear>ν</unclear>, ἄρτι δὲ <choice><reg>λίαν</reg><orig><unclear>λείαν</unclear></orig></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>χρ<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>ία αὐτοῦ ἐστιν. ἀνά

    <lb n="12" break="no"/>γνωθι οὖν Θάυτι τὴν 

    <lb n="13"/>ἐπιστολὴν, ἵνα εἰδῇ, ὅτι 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐγὼ αὐτοῦ χρείαν ἔχω 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ προτρέψῃ αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="16"/><choice><reg>ταχέως</reg><orig><unclear>τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">α</supplied><unclear>κχέ</unclear>ως</orig></choice> <unclear>παρ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">αγ</supplied>ε<unclear>ν</unclear>έ<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied>θαι. 

    <lb n="17"/>περὶ τῶν λίνων, 

    <lb n="18"/>ὧν χρείαν ἔλεγες 

    <lb n="19"/>ἔχειν, δήλωσόν μοι, ἵνα, 

    <lb n="20"/>ἐὰν ἔλθῃς, εὕρῃς αὐτά. 

    <lb n="21"/>δηλώσεις δὲ πάλιν εἰ 

    <lb n="22"/>Θᾶυς μέλλει ἔρχεσθαι 

    <lb n="23"/>πρὸς ἐμέ, ἵνα ἢ ἐπί

    <lb n="24" break="no"/>σχω αὐτῷ ἢ ἄλλον σκέψωμαι. 

    <lb n="25"/>ὡς νομ<supplied reason="lost">ί</supplied>ζω, οἶδεν ἡ γυνή 

    <lb n="26"/><app type="editorial"><lem resp="BGU 2 p.356"><subst><add place="inline">σου</add><del rend="corrected">μου</del></subst></lem><rdg><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>σου</rdg></app> ποῦ ἐστιν Θᾶυς, ἵνα εὕ

    <lb n="27" break="no"/>ρῃς αὐτόν. <handShift new="m2" cert="low"/> ἔρρωσθε <app type="editorial"><lem resp="PN N. Gonis (from image)">πανοικ<unclear>ε</unclear>ί.</lem><rdg><expan>πανοικ<ex>ίᾳ</ex></expan></rdg></app> 
